          "(If it rains, I'll stay home)",
          "",
          "Wenn du kommst, bin ich glücklich.",
          "(If you come, I'll be happy)",
          "",
          "STRUCTURE:",
          "wenn + subject + verb, main clause",
          "",
          "Use present tense in both clauses!",
          "German doesn't use future tense in wenn-clauses."
